==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: tribology
<hw>tri*bol"o*gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>tribo-</ets> + <ets>-ology</ets>.]</ety> <def>the study of
the effects of friction on parts of machinery moving in contact with
each other, and of methods, such as lubrication, to counteract negative
effects such as wear.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

